      <title>亿万富翁 Birla 预计其消费业务未来 5 年将增长至 250 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/billionaire-birla-sees-consumer-business-growing-to-25-billion-in-next-5-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁库玛尔·曼格拉姆·贝拉 (Kumar Mangalam Birla) 预计，随着他开始在全球第二大黄金市场销售黄金首饰，其价值 650 亿美元的金属到时尚集团的消费业务将在未来五年内增长到 250 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/billionaire-birla-sees-consumer-business-growing-to-25-billion-in-next-5-years</guid>
